name: Romantic Bosphorus - Multicolor - Wall Finishes
description: This multicolor design was painted in our studio after a lithograph printed in the 1850s by the Maltese artist Jean-Giovanni Schranz. We decided to make a full “verdure” out of it, omitting characters and simplifying buildings to create a much greener and sparer Bosphorus than that of the time, emphasizing the stunning nature and topography. Available in 5 heights. Designed by Iksel, and distributed exclusively by Schumacher in US and Canada.
